Results.ReviewText: As nescafe coffee drinkers on seeing nescafe gold we thought we would give it a try. We were delighted with the aroma and taste and would deffinately purchase it again
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: I really like the richness and depth of flavour of this coffee. I don't find it too overpowering, so it's a nice way to wake me up every day before I set off for work.
Results.Title: Rich and aromatic

Results.ReviewText: Have always been a fan of Nescafe Gold and really enjoyed the flavour of this coffee, however slight sediment (coffee dust) at the end of the cup is quite off putting.
Results.Title: Brilliant flavour

Results.ReviewText: When you open the jar the aroma is like 'fresh ground coffee'. I drink mine black and although a little more expensive than 'standard' Nescafe, the taste is excellent.
Results.Title: The enjoyment starts with the Aroma

Results.ReviewText: i always go for the gold try lots of coffees till I try Gold and finally found a strong smoothing great full body taste will take a lot for me to try let alone change
Results.Title: strong smooth great taste

Results.ReviewText: My husband and I always buy this coffee and I drink 3 cups of it per day.  It is always so delicious and thirst quenshing.  It wakes me up first thing in the morning.
Results.Title: Marvellous Coffee

Results.ReviewText:
i love coffee and it is the only hot drink i drink.
this is the best.
i only wish they hadn't changed the jar and labels because it now looks like other coffee jars
Results.Title: best instant coffee ever

Results.ReviewText: I’ve been drinking gold blend for years and their is no other coffee that can beat it the best coffee in the world , best blended coffee would not drink anything else
Results.Title: Greatest coffee

Results.ReviewText: Often buy this coffee to supplement the Nescafe Original that is my standard brew. Save it for when I feel like a treat. By far the best instant coffee on the market.
Results.Title: Best of the instants

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe Gold Blend has always been my regular, however, although the taste is as good I don't like the powdery residue left at the bottom of my mug with the new jars!
Results.Title: Same taste, however.......

Results.ReviewText: This coffee is my definite favourite. Beautiful flavour - gentle yet complete. If you haven't tried it yet, it is a must. Better than the best coffee shops can offer!
Results.Title: Proper coffee!

Results.ReviewText: I have always used Nescafé gold and loved it . The new product leaves a residue at the bottom of the mug which I do not like . Has the product been changed that much.
Results.Title: Leftovers

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking gold blend for 10 years, I love the smooth taste, and waking up to the great aroma coming from my cup. Love the new design. Keep up the good work
Results.Title: Julie

Results.ReviewText: Gold... I not only buy Nescafe Gold for home, buy I buy it for my work of place, so we get few quite a few jars in a month, but like the Olympics we are out for Gold
Results.Title: Olympic Coffee

Results.ReviewText: I have bought Gold Blend for so long now; I prefer it's taste to other "shop own" brands.  However, just lately it has just started to dissolve less well in the cup.
Results.Title: Gold Blend - jewel of coffees

Results.ReviewText: Recently we have noticed a lot of "dregs" left in the bottom of the mug once the drink in finished. This doesn't distract from the flavour, but is a bit off putting.
Results.Title: changed formula ?

Results.ReviewText: Since trying this coffee I have never had another type. I loved ordinary Nescafe but this is just that bit richer tasting and milder. It's the one for me from now on
Results.Title: Just great coffee

Results.ReviewText: Morrison had on special offer so filled up my cupboard love the new jar. contents still the same very high class coffee as good as any filter take mine black love it
Results.Title: neat jar

Results.ReviewText: I purchased this a few weeks ago and was not disappointed.  This coffee has a lovely smooth taste and is easy drinking. The quality is excellent. What’s not to like?
Results.Title: Smooth tasting

Results.ReviewText: I've gone through all the expensive coffee machines and back to good old instant. Just can't beat the rich coffee flavour especially with a nice big slab of cake YUM
Results.Title: Scrumptious with cake

Results.ReviewText: First impressions left me feeling that this was a great cup of coffee with a lovely subtle Fresh Brew taste giving it that true Coffee Flavour of a Continental Cafe.
Results.Title: A lovely Fresh Brew Tasting Coffee

Results.ReviewText: After I was unable to get my regular brand of coffee  I tried  Nescafe Gold and how glad I was, such rich full flavour. Nescafe Gold has now become my regular brand
Results.Title: rich full taste

Results.ReviewText: I bought this product with my most recent grocery order.It is the perfect coffee for a morning when I'm up early and my children are awake and their lively selves.
Results.Title: Lovely taste

ClientResponses.Response: We're always wanting our consumers to have the best experience, therefore we've added micro ground coffee to our NESCAFÉ Gold Blend to give it a richer aroma and a more intense roasted flavour.  It's sad to hear you don't like the new recipe but thank you for letting us know.

Results.ReviewText: My husband and I have been buying gold blend for years and now you have changed the taste it is awful why did you do that we will now be looking for an alternative
Results.Title: Changed taste

Results.ReviewText: I usually drink Nescafe Original but they have just started buying Gold Blend at work. I'm now sold - it's one of the best coffees I've had. Keep it coming Nescafe
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: I like to make latte with this with freshly boiled milk.  The builders have also said how much they like the coffee so it must taste good even with 2 large sugars.
Results.Title: Smooth and cream flavour

Results.ReviewText: Have drunk copious amounts of Gold Blend over 'many' years but I have gone the dark side and am newly addicted to Black!!! Avid black coffee drinkers dreammm. Xxxx
Results.Title: Fantastic rich flavour

Results.ReviewText: I BOUGHT MY FIRST NESCAFE GOLD BLEND LAST CHRISTMAS TO IMPRESS THE FAMILY AND FROM THE FIRST CUP I WAS HOOKED! PERFECT COFFEE ALWAYS AND EXACTLY THE TASTE I LOVE.
Results.Title: PERFECTION EVERY TIME!

Results.ReviewText: I wasn't happy with the brand I'd been buying for a while so tried Gold Blend a few months back and I love it. JUst the right taste for me, smooth and not bitter.
Results.Title: Lovely smooth coffee

Results.ReviewText: This is the only coffee I will drink...always have it with me ...my brother in America even ordered me some in on a recent visit...love it ..love it..love it !! X
Results.Title: Rich and smooth
